---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-950">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
			<div class="max-w-md">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-white">OpenAttitude</p>
				<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
					Web cockpit panels and reusable FlightGear instruments. Seneca II fgpanel is GPL-3.0-or-later;
					<code class="rounded bg-slate-900 px-1 py-0.5 text-cyan-300/90">@openattitude/*</code> packages
					on npm are LGPL-3.0-or-later.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 text-sm">
				<div>
					<p class="font-medium text-slate-300">Resources</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
						<li>
							<a href="/docs" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Documentation</a>
						</li>
						<li>
							<a
								href="https://www.npmjs.com/search?q=%40openattitude"
								class="hover:text-cyan-400"
								target="_blank"
								rel="noopener noreferrer">npm scope</a
							>
						</li>
						<li>
							<a
								href="https://senecaii.openattitude.org"
								class="hover:text-cyan-400"
								target="_blank"
								rel="noopener noreferrer">Live panel</a
							>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<p class="font-medium text-slate-300">FlightGear</p>
					<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
						<li>
							<a
								href="https://www.flightgear.org/"
								class="hover:text-cyan-400"
								target="_blank"
								rel="noopener noreferrer">FlightGear</a
							>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<p class="mt-10 border-t border-slate-800 pt-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-500">
			© {year} Torsten Dreyer &lt;torsten@t3r.de&gt;. Documentation on this site summarizes the public
			design of the panel and npm packages; see each repository for canonical license text.
		</p>
	</div>
</footer>
